Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Get Predictions in CRM Analytics Recipes

Use the Discovery Predict transformation to populate CRM Analytics datasets with predictions, top predictors, and improvements. The transformation requires a deployed model.

Users must have View Einstein Discovery Recommendations permission to view predictions, improvements, and related details.

To configure predictions and improvements, see Discovery Predict Transformation: Get Einstein Discovery Predictions.
title: Configuring Predictions in CRM Analytics Recipes
